- Use yarn as the package manager.
- Run periodically the yarn typecheck to make sure that everything is fine.
- Run yarn prepare to bundle again the library and update example app.
- Try always to create scalable, reliable and self-descriptive code.
- Always try to add JSDoc to the functions, methods, and other things.
- Don't leave comments that doesn't generate any value.
- The library doesn't have a version published, so we don't need backward compatibility.
- Don't worry about formatting.